Some words.

endemo2.execution

This package holds all modules that contribute to the actual execution of the program.

endemo2.general

This package holds modules that are relevant across all sectors.

endemo2.industry

This package holds all modules that are only relevant for the industry sector.

endemo2.input

This package holds all modules that contribute to reading the input files.

endemo2.sectors

This package holds all the modules directly representing a sector.

endemo2.utility

This package holds all modules that can be reused in very different contexts, therefore being utility.
